@startuml RDR Data Flow
!theme plain
title RDR — Поток данных: оборудование → запись → UI

actor User as user
participant "MainController\n(UI)" as MC
participant "RoastRecorder" as RR
participant "SamplingEngine" as SE
participant "RoastDataSource\n(Besca/Diedrich/Simulator)" as DS
participant "RoastProfile\n(domain)" as RP
participant "CurveChartFx\n(JFreeChart)" as Chart

== Подключение ==
user -> MC : Connect (настройки из Settings)
MC -> RR : connect()
RR -> DS : connect()
DS --> RR : connectionState() → Connected
RR --> MC : stateFlow = MONITORING

== Начало записи ==
user -> MC : Start
MC -> RR : startRecording()
RR -> RR : new RoastProfile()
RR -> SE : start { sample -> profile.addSample(sample) }
SE -> DS : sampleFlow().collect()

loop Каждый опрос (pollingIntervalMs)
  DS -> DS : read BT/ET registers (MODBUS) or simulate
  DS --> SE : emit TemperatureSample(timeSec, bt, et)
  SE -> RP : addSample(sample)
  RP --> RR : currentProfile updated
  RR --> MC : currentProfile.asStateFlow()
  MC -> Chart : обновить кривые (timex, temp1, temp2)
  Chart --> user : отрисовка графика
end

== События и комментарии ==
user -> MC : Event (Charge / FC / Drop) или Comment
MC -> RR : profile.addEvent() / addComment()
RR -> RP : append to events / comments
MC -> Chart : fireCurveChanged()
Chart --> user : маркеры на графике

== Управление (gas/air/drum) ==
user -> MC : Slider / Button
MC -> DS : setControl(id, value)  [если RoastControl]
note right of DS : MODBUS write register/coil

== Остановка ==
user -> MC : Stop
MC -> RR : stopRecording()
RR -> SE : stop()
SE -> DS : cancel collect
MC -> MC : Save profile (ProfileStorage) / Finish dialog

@enduml
